ST ETEC (the lower value of ETEC_STh and ETEC_STp)
LT ETEC (if ST ETEC=35, the value of ETEC_LT)
Atypical EPEC (if tEPEC = 35 and stec_stx1 = 35 and stec_stx2 = 35, then the value of EPEC_eae)
Shiga toxin producing E.coli (the lower value of STEC_stx1 and STEC_stx2)
